ss-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.1.options.3.text":"1,2,3","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.2.options.0.text":"1,2,4","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.2.options.1.text":"2,3,4","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.2.options.2.text":"1,2,3,4","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.2.options.3.text":"1,2,3","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.3.options.0.text":"Responsabilidad Social Corporativa Política","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.3.options.1.text":"Triple Resultado","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.3.options.2.text":"Sostenibilidad","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.3.options.3.text":"Ciudadanía corporativa","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.4.options.0.text":"1,2,3","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.4.options.1.text":"1,2,4","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.4.options.2.text":"1,3,4","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.4.options.3.text":"2,3,4","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.5.options.0.text":"Derechos corporativos, Efecto corporativo, Parte interesada","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.5.options.1.text":"Negación corporativa, Efecto corporativo, Parte interesada","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.5.options.2.text":"Derechos corporativos, Responsabilidad corporativa, Parte interesada","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.5.options.3.text":"Derechos corporativos, Efecto corporativo, Accionista","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.6.options.0.text":"Increíblemente cercano, de hecho, en todos los casos lo que es ético también es lo que es legal y viceversa.","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.6.options.1.text":"No cercano, la ética y la ley comparten una pequeña cantidad de superposición, pero abordan fundamentalmente preguntas y temas diferentes.","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.6.options.2.text":"Cercano, ya que hay una considerable superposición entre ética y ley, pero los dos no son equivalentes.","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.6.options.3.text":"En absoluto cercano, la ética y la ley son prácticamente incompatibles.","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.7.options.0.text":"Profesional, Organizacional, Personal, Organizacional","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.7.options.1.text":"Profesional, Individual, Personal, Organizacional","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.7.options.2.text":"Individual, Organizacional, Organizacional, Profesional","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.7.options.3.text":"Individual, Profesional, Organizacional, Personal","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.8.options.0.text":"Informes anuales, Desempeño financiero de la empresa","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.8.options.1.text":"Informe anual, Internet - redes sociales y networking","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.8.options.2.text":"Códigos de ética, Desempeño financiero de la empresa","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.8.options.3.text":"Códigos de ética, Internet - redes sociales y networking","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.9.options.0.text":"La ética empresarial no es un concepto real ya que las reglas y la ética de la vida cotidiana no se aplican al mundo de los negocios.","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.9.options.1.text":"La ética empresarial es el estudio de situaciones, actividades y decisiones empresariales donde se abordan cuestiones de bien y mal.","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.9.options.2.text":"La ética empresarial no puede definirse como un concepto real ya que es un término oxímoron.","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.9.options.3.text":"La ética empresarial se ocupa del estudio de la evaluación de las actividades de un negocio en función de su rentabilidad.","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.10.options.0.text":"Ley de Venta de Bienes de 1979","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.10.options.1.text":"Ley de Servicios Financieros de 1986","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.10.options.2.text":"Ley de Sociedades de 2006 y Ley de Insolvencia de 1986","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.10.options.3.text":"Ley de Salud y Seguridad en el Trabajo de 1974","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.11.options.0.text":"Económico, Competencia comercial, Sanción social","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.11.options.1.text":"Político, Regulación indeseable, Retiro transnacional","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.11.options.2.text":"Social, Competencia comercial, Sanción social","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.11.options.3.text":"Social, Regulación indeseable, Retiro transnacional","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.12.options.0.text":"1,3","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.12.options.1.text":"2,3","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.12.options.2.text":"1,2","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.12.options.3.text":"1,2,3","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.13.options.0.text":"Filantropía, OSC, Empresas sociales","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.13.options.1.text":"Filantropía, Gobierno, Grupos de cabildeo","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.13.options.2.text":"Campañas publicitarias, OSC, Grupos de cabildeo","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.13.options.3.text":"Campañas publicitarias, Gobierno, Empresas sociales","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.14.options.0.text":"Relación de agencia, Agente, Principales","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.14.options.1.text":"Gestión de interesados, Agente, Principales","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.14.options.2.text":"Relación de agencia, Principal, Agentes","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l07:questions.14.options.3.text":"Gestión de interesados, Principal, Agentes","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:title":"Ética empresarial — Cuestionario 8","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.0.options.0.text":"1,4","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.0.options.1.text":"1,3","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.0.options.2.text":"2,3","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.0.options.3.text":"1,2,3","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.1.options.0.text":"1,2,4","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.1.options.1.text":"1,3,4","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.1.options.2.text":"2,3,4","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.1.options.3.text":"1,2,3,4,5","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.2.options.0.text":"'Plan A' de Marks & Spencer","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.2.options.1.text":"'Objetivos de Desarrollo Sostenible' de las Naciones Unidas","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.2.options.2.text":"'Iniciativas de Sostenibilidad' del Grupo Alibaba","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.2.options.3.text":"'Plan de Vida Sostenible' de Unilever","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.3.options.0.text":"La propiedad y el control están separados","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.3.options.1.text":"Los gerentes siempre actúan en su propio interés","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.3.options.2.text":"La maximización de beneficios es el principal objetivo de las organizaciones","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.3.options.3.text":"Los interesados tienen diferentes niveles de poder","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.4.options.0.text":"Responsabilidad Social Corporativa","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.4.options.1.text":"Responsabilidad Social de la Empresa","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.4.options.2.text":"Responsabilidad Social Corporativa","mba-business-ethics-u1-external-l08:questions.4.options.3.text":"Respon